approveCapExProposal(uint256).details: Convenience function to approve CapEx proposal

params.reserveThreshold: Minimum reserve to keep in RentVault

createCapExProposal(uint256,string).details: Convenience function to create CapEx proposal

depositRent(uint256).details: Convenience function to deposit rent Note: Caller must approve USDC to the rent vault, not this contract

getTotalAssetsInVault().details: Get total assets in yield vault

getYieldEarned().details: Get yield earned from DeFi vault

initialize((string,uint256,uint256,strin.details: Initialize the entire system with a new property

params._totalShares: Total number of shares to mint
params.initialShareholder: Address to receive all initial shares

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

recordOperatingExpense(uint256).details: Convenience function to record operating expense

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

resetPeriod().details: Reset period (calls both rent vault and cash flow engine)

setManager(address).details: Set manager for cash flow engine

setYieldVault(address).details: Set the ERC-4626 vault address for yield stacking

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.
